Package com.fdmgroup.banking

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Bank
    The Bank Account Class is in charge of keeping track of all the customers within each bank and accounts without an owner.
    BankAccount
    BankAccount is an ABSTRACT CLASS that contains the general information contained within each Banking/Checking Accounts regardless of Business/Personal use.
    BankCustomer
    BankCustomer is an ABSTRACT CLASS that contains the general information contained within each Business/Personal use.
    BusinessChecking
    The BusinessChecking Class specifies the functionality/ability for Checking Accounts owned by Businesses.
    BusinessSaving
    The BusinessSaving Class specifies the functionality/ability for Saving Accounts owned by Businesses.
    CheckingAcc
    CheckingAcc is an ABSTRACT CLASS that describes the functionality/ability of Checking Accounts.
    Company
    The Company Class specifies the functionality/ability for Businesses/Companies.
    FDIC
    FDIC is the Main Class which tests the Bank Design Project.
    Person  
    PersonalChecking
    PersonalChecking Class specifies the functionality/ability for Checking Accounts owned by Businesses.
    PersonalSaving
    PersonalSaving Class specifies the functionality/ability for Saving Accounts owned by Businesses.
    SavingAcc
    SavingAcc is an ABSTRACT CLASS that describes the functionality/ability of Saving Accounts.
    SingleAccounter
    SingleAccounter is a Singleton Class for keeping track of Accounting ID's.
    SingleCuscounter
    SingleCuscounter is a Singleton Class for keeping track of Customer ID's.
